member.name: Samir Durvasula

However, while most project teams are overly competition focused, and EWH has a significant service focus. I was looking for a project team that truly tries to make a difference in the world. EWH is an example of this mission, while still participating in a desing competition every year. In addition, some of my closest friends are on the EWH team, making it a great community!
